    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ所属アイドル合同ライブ、当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of joint live by idols in Hoshimi Productions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……うっ、始まった……\n始まって、しまった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Uh‚ it's starting…\nIt's starting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3,
      "endTime": 7.262630399000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "緊張してるの？　雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you nervous‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6,
      "endTime": 9.9499999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、今日は、私達がファンの前で初めて歌う……\n情報は一切出してない、完全なサプライズ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes‚ today is the first time we'll sing in front of the fans…\nWe haven't released any information‚ it's a complete surprise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "endTime": 22.4925570806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 22.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの、反応が、怖いです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm scared of everyone's reaction…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "endTime": 26.4141497612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 26.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、私もトリエルとしてステージに上がるのと\n違う緊張感があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. It's different from going on stage as TRINITYAiLE.\nIt has a unique nervousness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "endTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言いながら……楽しそう、です\nさすが、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you say that… You look like you're having fun.\nAs expected… of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5,
      "endTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 39.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "やるべきことは全てやったわ、私もあなたも\nだから大丈夫。……まだ自信、ない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've done everything we needed to do‚ both you and me.\nSo it'll be fine… Still not confident?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "endTime": 48.833333333300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 49.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "最初はなかった\n……けど、今はある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I wasn't confident.\n…But now‚ I am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0666666667,
      "endTime": 55.542686972999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんといっぱい、話して、いっぱい、練習したから\n…………練習は、裏切らない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I talked a lot and practiced a lot with Rui-san.\n……… Practice never betrays you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7333333333,
      "endTime": 64.03333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 64.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。今まで頑張ってきた自分を信じて、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Believe in yourself‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2333333333,
      "endTime": 69.18340113949999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 69.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "信じます、自分と……瑠依さんを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe in myself… and in Rui-san too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "endTime": 73.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "前から思っていたんだけど\nそろそろさん付けはやめない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been thinking about it for a while‚ but\nCan you stop using \"-san\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1,
      "endTime": 78.3054700616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 78.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私達、同じユニットのメンバーでしょ\n対等な関係なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're members of the same team‚ right?\nWe're in an equal relationship.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5,
      "endTime": 83.8389409425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 84.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……難しいです……\n今までの、どの練習より、一番大変……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's… difficult…\nMore challenging than any practice we've done before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0333333333,
      "endTime": 92.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 92.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、じゃあ、これから沢山練習しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ then let's practice that a lot from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5666666667,
      "endTime": 96.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、瑠依ちゃん、そろそろ出番だよ\n準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ Rui-chan‚ it's almost time for your turn.\nAre you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666666667,
      "endTime": 102.61,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 97.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 102.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、しっかりなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you‚ stay strong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "endTime": 105.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 105.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで応援してるからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll be cheering for you together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4333333333,
      "endTime": 107.4245124896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、みんな\n行きましょう、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ everyone.\nLet's go‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333333333,
      "endTime": 111.7978151583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_06-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "はい……！　瑠依さん\nじゃなくて、瑠依、ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…! Rui-san…\nNo‚ Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666666667,
      "endTime": 117.8333333334,
